headline: FormFactor (FORM): A Fresh Look at Valuation Following Sector-Wide Semiconductor Weakness Triggered by Texas Instruments’ Outlook
summary: FormFactor (FORM) shares declined nearly 5% after Texas Instruments issued a cautious outlook and a slight profit miss, which dampened sentiment throughout the semiconductor sector. The move highlights how industry forecasts can ripple across peers. See our latest analysis for FormFactor. FormFactor’s share price has rebounded impressively in recent weeks, rising over 15% in the past month despite broader chip sector volatility.
